OL,3,CCoastal community hit by sewage spills
OL,4,Clooks at legal action against water
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,FBusinesses and residents in the Devon
OL,8,Ftown of Exmouth have appointed a legal
OL,9,Ffirm to investigate a claim against
OL,10,FSouth West Water.
OL,12,FIt comes after a series of no-swim
OL,13,Fwarnings follows a number of sewage
OL,14,Fspills on the beach.
OL,16,FA group of businesses say the beach
OL,17,Fclosures have resulted in a large fall
OL,18,Fin sales over the summer months.
