OL,7,FTogether they have asked lawyers Leigh
OL,8,FDay to look into what legal action is
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,FLeigh Day solicitor Benji Gourgey
OL,12,Fsaid: "Leigh Day represents wild
OL,13,Fswimmer Jo Bateman in her claim
OL,14,Fagainst South West Water over sewage
OL,15,Fpollution affecting Exmouth Beach
OL,16,Fwhich means she is often unable to
OL,17,Fswim in the sea.
