OL,7,F"We are also working closely with the
OL,8,Fwider community and are investigating
OL,9,Fpossible legal solutions to the
OL,10,Fongoing sewage pollution that is
OL,11,Fimpacting Exmouth as a whole."
OL,13,FSouth West Water said the problems
OL,14,Fthis summer have been the result of a
OL,15,Fburst sewage pipe in the town and
OL,16,Frepair work is underway. The company
OL,17,Fsays it is investing nearly 40 million
OL,18,Fpounds in the Exmouth area over the
OL,19,Fnext six years.
