OL,7,FThe leader of East Devon District
OL,8,FCouncil has described the on-going
OL,9,Fpollution issues at Exmouth Beach as
OL,10,F'a civil emergency'. Councillor Paul
OL,11,FArnott has said he believes the
OL,12,FGovernment should step in and sort out
OL,13,Fthe issue.
