OL,7,FSouth West Water said: "We are serious
OL,8,Fabout tackling storm overflows and
OL,9,Fchange of this scale takes time,
OL,10,Fambition, and increased investment. We
OL,11,Fare investing around #38 million in
OL,12,Fthe Exmouth area up to 2030 which
OL,13,Fincludes upgrades to our pumping
OL,14,Fstations and treatment works to
OL,15,Fsignificantly reduce the number of
OL,16,Fspills and further protect the
OL,17,Fenvironment."
